title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA -  The Breakers
description:
In this video we will fly over The Breakers. The Breakers is a Gilded Age mansion located at 44 Ochre Point Avenue, Newport, Rhode Island, US. It was built between 1893 and 1895 as a summer residence for Cornelius Vanderbilt II, a member of the wealthy Vanderbilt family.
